thread.title: Chris
thread.title_full: Freeze Pro Shop reviewed by Chris

author: Chris
title: Chris
text:
Freeze have got a pretty solid thing going on and I couldn't fault their service. I live in Australia, last order was placed on a Friday night and it arrived in my hands a few days later on the Monday...couldn't believe how quick it was. This is the second of two orders both of which have been seamless, even down to their nice and neat packaging.
Again, couldn't fault the service or price. Will be buying from here in future.
